 304:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   The PWR_LDO_SUPPLY and PWR_EXTERNAL_SOURCE_SUPPLY are used by all
